# signal-lab — legacy .cursorrules fallback
Stack: NestJS (port 4000) + Next.js App Router (port 3000) + PostgreSQL + Prisma
Observability: prom-client + winston-loki + @sentry/node + Grafana + Loki + Prometheus
All infrastructure via Docker Compose only.
Never use console.log in backend — always NestJS Logger.
All metrics prefixed signal_lab_. All logs structured JSON with scenarioId + scenarioType.
Every scenario run fires all 4 signals: counter + log + prisma persist + sentry (if error).
If request is ambiguous: state interpretation and ask before coding.
Surgical edits only — don't touch code outside the scope of the request.
